Package: snapr
Title: Convenient Snapshot Testing Functions for R Packages
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Douglas Ezra", "Morrison", , "demorrison@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides convenient snapshot testing functions for R packages,
    including expect_snapshot_data() for data.frames and 
    expect_snapshot_object() for any R object.
